OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTop US court halts Texas   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fexecution of inmate seeking
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fpastor's touch             
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The US Supreme Court has stayed the    
OL,6, execution of Texas inmate John Henry   
OL,7, Ramirez, who requested the right to    
OL,8, have his pastor hold him as he died.   
OL,10,FRamirez argued a Texas policy of not   
OL,11,Fallowing spiritual advisers to touch   
OL,12,Finmates during execution violated his  
OL,13,Fright to practise religion.            
OL,15,FPrison officials have said the rule is 
OL,16,Fin place "due to security concerns".   
OL,18,FIn an order on Wednesday, the top court
OL,19,Fsaid the justices would take up the    
OL,20,Fappeal in October or November.         
